
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

  	<head>
		<title>OAuth2orize Provider Example</title>
		<link href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.1.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" id="bootstrap-css">
		<script src="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.1.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
		<script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>
  	</head>

  	<body>
      <div class="container">
        <div id="loginbox" style="margin-top:50px;" class="mainbox col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
            <div class="panel panel-info" >
			    <form id="loginform" action="/auth/oauth2/authorize/decision" class="form-horizontal" role="form" method="post">
                    <input name="transaction_id" type="hidden" value="<%= transactionId %>" />

                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <div class="panel-title">Petición de acceso a la aplicación <b>Test domain 1</b> </div>
                    </div>
            
                    <div style="padding-top:30px" class="panel-body" >
                        <div style="display:none" id="login-alert" class="alert alert-danger col-sm-12"></div>
                       
                           <p>Hola <b><%= user.firstName %></b>, la aplicación <b> Test domain 1</b> solicita permisos para acceder a:</p>
                           <p> - tu nombre y apellidos </p>
                           <p> - tu correo </p>
                          <input type="submit" value="Aceptar"  id="allow" />


                        </div>
                    </div>
        </div>
    </div>

	</body>

</html>
